`GlobalEventExecutor#takeTask` is blocking. Since it is required to run the event loop, you should whitelist it. Here are some tips on how and what to whitelist:
https://github.com/reactor/BlockHound/blob/85a1bcfb2ea41035474a50f92ac0c050597335aa/docs/tips.md#how-to-select-what-to-whitelist

